Yes, I did.

38:45.524 --> 38:46.725
But for
a legitimate reason.

38:46.758 --> 38:49.495
There was a gun in the house,
but that's not the point.

38:49.528 --> 38:52.598
The point is that,
in the midst of all of this...

38:52.631 --> 38:55.233
